snippet.title: Case #1 Mysteries of the Past: “Welcome to Concordia!"
snippet.description:
★ NEW CASE: MYSTERIES OF THE PAST ★ Murder on the docks! Native Concordians clash with Irish immigrants in pursuit of the American dream… and things take a turn for the worse when a man is found poisoned! Can you catch the killer and give them one-way ticket to prison?

http://2sm.pl/2fA5MYI -- Investigate Now!
